loadeR.2nc
==========

## v0.0.0 (22 Feb 2016)
* First package release

## v0.0.1 (23 Feb 2016)
* Bug fix in date definition, affecting monthly datasets only

## v0.0.2 (9 Feb 2018)
* Bug fix in the placement of global attributes
* Update installed example dataset to convey the current climate4R grid attributes and reduce its size
* Other minor documentation updates

## v0.1.0 (5 Jul 2018)
* New function to export climate4R station object grids

## v0.1.1 (24 Feb 2020)
* Allow member dimension writing as character
* Other enhancements

## v1.0.0 (25 May 2021)
* New variable attribute list structure to include attribute precision (No backwards compatibility!)
* Force nc_close on exit
* Allow overwriting variable attributes "long_name", "name" and "units" by optional globalAttributes argument values
* Other minor internal changes and documentation updates


